---
title: Golden Halloumi, Clementine and Pea Salad with Toasted Pepitas and Balsamic Glaze
description: Juicy, sweet clementine takes centre stage in this weeknight salad. Halloumi, pepitas, balsamic glaze and DIY croutons feature as the delicious supporting cast!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salade-de-clementines-de-pois-et-de-halloumi-54aee30f.jpg
